results.name: Number of polyominoes consisting of 9 regular unit n-gons.
link: Matthias Koch and Sascha Kurz, Enumeration of generalized polyominoes, preprint, arXiv:math.CO/0605144
example: a(3)=160 because there are 160 polyiamonds consisting of 9 triangles and a(4)=1285 because there are 1285 polyominoes consisting of 9 squares.
